blueprint_book.label: [font=count-font][color=acid]Mixed Elev. Cityblock[/color][/font]
blueprint_book.description:
If you want a smaller/bigger grid, you're welcome to make it exactly how you want... yourself :)
Admittedly, this is a bit of a proof of concept for mixed elevation tracks.

Only every 3rd endpoint will align with regular grid rail. Will always align with hypermodular rails.
